description:
This is a 6 minute workout called 'Hydrow Games: Post-Row Yoga Restore' from the channel Owen Henn.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Reboot Workout and The Deep Recharge vibe.
The The Reboot Workout vibe means Deep stretch, low stress, total-body refresh. This is especially good for Recovery days, stress relief, post-travel stiffness. The The Deep Recharge vibe means Nervous system reset, ultra-gentle movement. This is especially good for Times of extreme stress, fatigue, or mental overload..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Recover and rejuvenate with Owen in this soothing 5-minute Yoga Restore session, perfect for unwinding after an intense row in the Hydrow Games. Focus on easing tension and steadying your breath as you move through gentle stretches and restorative poses. Embrace the moment of gratitude for showing up and putting in the effort. This post-row yoga will restore you and prepare you for your next challenge....
